{"ts":"2026-07-21T09:58:31.943Z","sessionId":"s_f0f4e55d","event":"task_complete","detail":"Phase 1 complete: project scaffolding and build system. Created core/ (11 headers + 15 sources), csllm/ Python package, train/, gateway/, tests/, configs/. CMakeLists.txt with Accelerate discovery and three-tier pybind11 resolution; pyproject.toml via scikit-build-core so `pip install -e .` compiles the C++. Implemented GEMM (Accelerate + naive fallback), arena allocator, thread pool, autograd tape, config validation, cosine LR, and KV cache for real; model math stubbed for Phase 2. Verified: build green, 13 tests pass, 0 compiler warnings, ruff clean, Accelerate active, fast-math off, C++20, shakespeare config = 12,194,688 params, GEMM matches NumPy.","meta":{"taskId":"t_f521149b","updatedFiles":["phase","memory"]}}
{"ts":"2026-07-21T10:08:34.223Z","sessionId":"s_f0f4e55d","event":"task_begin","detail":"Phase 2: implement the C++ core — tensor allocation, tape autograd wiring, matmul, RMSNorm, RoPE, causal softmax, SiLU/SwiGLU, embedding, fused cross-entropy, fused causal multi-head attention, the model with weight tying, AdamW with grad clipping, the sampler, .csllm serialization, and the expanded pybind11 surface. Every op gated on a NumPy oracle and a double-precision gradcheck.","meta":{"taskId":"t_872cf28d"}}
