{"ts":"2026-07-21T11:48:11.702Z","sessionId":"s_f0f4e55d","event":"task_complete","detail":"CSLLM 2.0 Phase 1 complete. Built the datasets/ plugin system (DatasetPlugin ABC with __init_subclass__ auto-registration, extension-keyed registry, discover/describe/iter_documents, and built-in .txt/.md, .jsonl/.ndjson, .csv/.tsv readers that fail with file+line on malformed input). Added optional special-token support to the BPE tokenizer (inert unless allow_special=True, ids persisted explicitly so a truncated merge list cannot shift them, single-document path byte-identical). Added encode_documents()/prepare_dataset() inserting the EOT separator between documents only. Wrote csllm/export.py producing model.safetensors + tokenizer.json + config.json via the safetensors numpy backend — no torch, keeping rules.md rule #1 intact. Added make export/datasets targets (both .PHONY, since a datasets/ directory exists). 60 new tests -> 224 total, ruff clean, 0 compiler warnings. Verified by exporting the real trained 12M model: 56 tensors, 12,194,688 params, max abs difference 0.0 vs the live engine, bundle reconstructible with numpy+safetensors alone with torch never imported.","meta":{"taskId":"t_09e89c12","updatedFiles":["phase","memory"]}}
{"ts":"2026-07-21T17:06:23.053Z","sessionId":"s_f0f4e55d","event":"task_begin","detail":"CSLLM 2.0 Phase 2: C++ additions (attention capture on GenerationSession, bind decode(), refactor Sampler so sample() and a new distribution() share one filtering implementation), plus training telemetry (train.py --emit-jsonl, gateway TrainingSupervisor subprocess + WS fan-out, /train routes) and POST /configure_model with versioned config storage. Split the gateway into routers.","meta":{"taskId":"t_b3b36d96"}}
