{"ts":"2026-07-21T19:32:26.300Z","sessionId":"s_6cd6efac","event":"task_complete","detail":"CSLLM 3.0 Phase 1 — model configurator & parameter calculator. Added csllm/params.py (calculate_model_params: param breakdown + train-memory breakdown, swept against the C++ ModelConfig::num_params()), csllm/resources.py (probe_device: NVIDIA VRAM / Apple unified memory / RAM, no new deps), a side-effect-free POST /configure_model/estimate, ArchitectureParams as the shared request base, and the React ConfiguratorPanel tab (live count, stacked memory bar, headroom, version creation). PyTorch was declined per rule #1 and confirmed with the user. 350 Python + 49 frontend tests pass, ruff and tsc clean; verified live over CDP.","meta":{"taskId":"t_49ac75bf","updatedFiles":["phase","memory"]}}
