{"ts":"2026-07-21T20:01:39.606Z","sessionId":"s_6cd6efac","event":"task_complete","detail":"CSLLM 3.0 Phase 2 — training manager & dataset wiring. TrainingSupervisor generalized to job kinds (train|prepare) via a JOBS table; train_tokenizer gained --dataset (plugin registry) + --emit-jsonl with train/emit.py as the shared emitter; new POST /datasets/{name}/prepare, GET /prepared, POST /train/{pause,resume} using SIGSTOP/SIGCONT (with SIGCONT-before-SIGTERM so Stop does not hang); trainer emits epoch + rss_bytes and host memory facts; new DatasetBrowser tab and reworked TrainingDashboard (steps slider, prepared-data selector, pause/resume, epoch + memory sparkline); applyTrainEvent extracted for testability. Fixed: prepare output path collided with the shipped data/debug corpus (now data/prepared/<dataset>/), vocab_size read from the wrong place, and a failed RSS probe charted as zero. 377 Python + 60 frontend tests pass, ruff and tsc clean; verified live over CDP end to end.","meta":{"taskId":"t_3129cd07","updatedFiles":["phase","memory"]}}
